{"tid":338733,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"想做唔仆街既貓義工 有冇巴絲教路","createTime":"2017-07-28T12:10:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T12:54:26.000Z","uid":87388,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f978e1dcd498e6290d192a89d92667836f22391f","tid":338733,"uid":87388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T12:10:07.000Z","msg":"一直好鐘意貓 但係屋企唔養得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今年終於下定定心做貓義工 但係貓義工臭史連連 我又唔想做仆街貓義工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問下有冇比較了解呢方面既巴絲介紹邊到做比較好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上網見到較大型既有群貓會同spac<br />\n唔知呢d入到去會唔會做仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 冇對貓經驗 但係唔怕辛苦 污穢 都唔怕俾貓整親"},{"pid":"8fc1aa843db70ed5ee40b177ce48470753ed3071","tid":338733,"uid":87388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T12:10:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1428bcd72212199bc31f70adc9901e208a38719c","tid":338733,"uid":87388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T12:11:19.000Z","msg":"麻煩各位教路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"090d63f573ea1521bdac9937d765614ab225fb1c","tid":338733,"uid":19159,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T12:25:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一直好鐘意貓 但係屋企唔養得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今年終於下定定心做貓義工 但係貓義工臭史連連 我又唔想做仆街貓義工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問下有冇比較了解呢方面既巴絲介紹邊到做比較好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上網見到較大型既有群貓會同spac<br />\n唔知呢d入到去會唔會做仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 冇對貓經驗 但係唔怕辛苦 污穢 都唔怕俾貓整親</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都好中意貓 但唔一定要做仆街義工<br />\n我就自己間唔中執到貓會養住先 再搵人養 唔洗家訪 有心就好 但會keep住做朋友聯絡 傾下貓計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我會經常教養貓朋友揀糧揀砂揀罐揀玩具 甚至煮貓飯 點樣係最健康 最抵玩 最貼地 對佢地又最好。<br />\n前提係我真係睇好多貓書 爬文 而且養緊幾隻貓 都係領養同執返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n愛貓唔係口上說說 去下貓cafe 或者得閒做貓撚鬧人唔識養就係<br />\n真係要花心機睇書睇文去研究一切關於貓既野 <br />\n<br />\n愛貓有好多種方式 樓主要加油喔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以搵我傾貓計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30db17ac3459ebc87276a130a748fe6ffc98dbc7","tid":338733,"uid":281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T12:30:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d094f23a7b57f77026634c709bd123143e109d8a","tid":338733,"uid":87388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T12:41:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一直好鐘意貓 但係屋企唔養得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今年終於下定定心做貓義工 但係貓義工臭史連連 我又唔想做仆街貓義工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問下有冇比較了解呢方面既巴絲介紹邊到做比較好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上網見到較大型既有群貓會同spac<br />\n唔知呢d入到去會唔會做仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 冇對貓經驗 但係唔怕辛苦 污穢 都唔怕俾貓整親</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都好中意貓 但唔一定要做仆街義工<br />\n我就自己間唔中執到貓會養住先 再搵人養 唔洗家訪 有心就好 但會keep住做朋友聯絡 傾下貓計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我會經常教養貓朋友揀糧揀砂揀罐揀玩具 甚至煮貓飯 點樣係最健康 最抵玩 最貼地 對佢地又最好。<br />\n前提係我真係睇好多貓書 爬文 而且養緊幾隻貓 都係領養同執返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n愛貓唔係口上說說 去下貓cafe 或者得閒做貓撚鬧人唔識養就係<br />\n真係要花心機睇書睇文去研究一切關於貓既野 <br />\n<br />\n愛貓有好多種方式 樓主要加油喔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以搵我傾貓計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多謝你既回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我會努力用其他方法去實行愛貓呢件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得你講得好岩 要由爬同貓相關既文同書開始 我都會開始睇 希望就算領養唔到都可以幫到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n感謝回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n感受到你好愛貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我會加油"},{"pid":"b5172638d0dd9905604ed2b17fbbedd637c802bc","tid":338733,"uid":19159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T12:53:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果煮健康貓飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\ntg我啦"},{"pid":"1ed3ad447e3573cde0974b95c43e7e722323957d","tid":338733,"uid":19159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T12:54:26.000